seng202.team1.Model

Class WifiPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team1.Model.DataPoint
      • seng202.team1.Model.WifiPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class WifiPoint
extends DataPoint
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class for type of Wifi Points. Has a single constructor which sets all the values of the point. CSV files contain more points but these are the important ones for the app. All the methods in here are getters and setters (and toString).

                 java.time.LocalDateTime datetimeActivated)
        Constructor for WifiPoint
        Parameters:
        objectId - ID of object
        coords - co-ordinates of WiFi
        placeName - name of the place where the WiFi is - e.g. Wingate Park
        location - location of WiFi, usually an address
        locationType - type of location - e.g. Outdoor Kiosk
        hood - neighbourhood where WiFi is - e.g. Chinatown
        borough - borough where WiFi is
        city - city where WiFi is
        zipcode - ZIP code of where WiFi is
        cost - cost of WiFi (Free, Limited Free, or Partner Site)
        provider - provider of WiFi
        remarks - any remarks about the WiFi
        ssid - SSID of WiFi - this is the "name" of the WiFi a user sees on their device
        sourceId - Source ID of WiFi
        datetimeActivated - date and time the WiFi was activated
